  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC077">
        <l>aintā kuvatē,</l>
	<l>iṉṉeṉap peyariya vēṟṟumaik kiḷavi</l>
	<l>yitaṉi ṉiṟṟitu veṉṉu matuvē.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/59/mode/1up">59</ref>.</p>
      <p><note xml:lang="en">This verse and the next are considered one verse.</note></p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tāmōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n82/mode/1up">79</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n83/mode/1up">80</ref>.</p>
<p>i-ḷ. mēl iṉṉeṉap peyar koṭuttōtappaṭṭa vēṟṟumaiccol aintāvatām. aḵtu ipporuḷiṉittaṉmaittu ipporuḷeṉṉum poruṇmaiyai uṇarttum. e-ṟu.</p>
<p>aintāvatu nāṉkuporuṇmaiyuṭaittu; poruvum, ellaiyum, nīkkamum, ētuvumeṉa. avaṟṟuṭporuviruvakaippaṭum; uṟaḻporuvum, uvamapporuvumeṉa. ētuvumiruvakaippaṭum; ñāpakavētuvum, kārakavētuvumeṉa. avaṟṟuṇ ñāpakavētupporuṇmai mēlē kūṟappaṭṭatu. kārakavētupporuṇmai accamākkameṉpaṉavaṟṟāṟ peṟappaṭum. nīkkapporuṇmai tīrtal paṟṟuviṭutaleṉpaṉavaṟṟāṟpeṟappaṭum. ēṉaiyiraṇṭum itaṉiṉiṟṟituveṉpataṉāṟ koḷḷappaṭum, avviraṇṭaṉaiyum aḵtirumuṟaiyāṉuṇarttumākalāṉ. ellaipporuḷ - </p>
  <lg xml:id="TolC077-Cēṉ-cit1">
    karuvūriṉkiḻakku</lg><p>;</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC077-Cēṉ-cit2">
    itaṉiṉūṅku
  </lg> 
  <p>eṉa varum. kiḻakku ūṅkeṉpaṉa, viṉaikkuṟip pallavēṉum iṟṟeṉṉum poruḷpaṭa niṟṟaliṉ, iṟṟeṉṟalēyām. porūupporuṭkutāraṇam muṉṉarppeṟappaṭum.	(16)</p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/n123/mode/1up">95</ref>―<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/375/mode/1up">96</ref>.</p>
<p>
atu, muṟaiyāṉē aintāvatip poruṭkaṇ varumeṉkiṉṟatu.
</p>
<p>
(i-ḷ)
iṉṉeṉap peyariya vēṟṟumaik kiḷavi yaintākuvatē ― mēliṉṉeṉap peyar koṭuttōtiya vēṟṟumaic collain tāvatām; atu itaṉiṉiṟṟitu veṉṉum ― atu ipporuḷi ṉittaṉmaiyāyirukku mip poru ḷeṉṉum poruṇmaiyai yuṇarttu meṉṟavāṟu,
</p>
<p>
aintāvatu poruvu mellaiyum nīkkamu mētuvumeṉa nāṉku vakaippaṭum. uṟaḻ poruvu muvamapporuvu meṉaviruvakaippaṭum. uṟaḻta loṉṟaṉāṉoṉṟai mikuttal. ētuvu ñāpaka vētuvuṅ kāraka vētuvumeṉa viruvakaip paṭum. ñāpakavētu muṉ kūṟiṟṟu. kāraka vētu, vacca mākka meṉpaṉa vaṟṟāṟ peṟappaṭum. nīkkap poruṇmai, tīrtal paṟṟuviṭutaleṉpaṉavaṟṟāṟ peṟappaṭum. ēṉaiyiraṇṭumitaṉiṉiṟṟitu, veṉpataṉāṟ peṟappaṭum. avviraṇṭiṉaiyum aḵtiru muṟaiyāṉuṇartt umātaliṉ. ellaipporuḷ,
</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC077-Nacc-cit1">
  <l>karuvūriṉ kiḻakkivvūr</l>
</lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC077-Nacc-cit2">
 <l>itaṉi ṉūṅku</l>
 </lg>
      <p>
        eṉa varum. ivaiyu miṟṟeṉṉum poruṭṭu.  <num xml:lang="en">(16)</num>
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Teyvaccilaiyār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">1929, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n69/mode/1up">62</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n70/mode/1up">70</ref>.</p>
      <p>
aintām vēṟṟumai yāmāṟu uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
        i-ḷ: ―
        aintām vēṟṟumaiyāvatu iṉ eṉṟu peyar koṭut tōtappaṭṭa vēṟṟumaiccol. aḵtu ipporuḷiṉ ittaṉmaittu ipporuḷ eṉa uṇarttum. e. ṟu. eṉavē ivvāypāṭṭāṉ varum poruṇmai yellām aintāvatām. e-ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
        avaiyāvaṉa:- nīṅka niṟpatūum, poruvum, ētuvum eṉ(paṉa.) avaṟṟuḷ nīṅka niṟpatu poruḷ nīṅki niṟpatūum, iṭam nīṅki niṟpatūum eṉa iruvakaippaṭum. poruvum mikutalum, kuṟaitalum, ottalum eṉa mūṉṟu vakaippaṭum. avaṟṟuḷ poruvum, ētuvum varukiṉṟa cūttirattāl kūṟutalāṉum, palporuṭ kēṟpiṉ nallatu kōṭal eṉpataṉāṉum iccūttiram nīṅka niṟpatu kuṟittateṉpatu koḷḷappaṭum.	
      </p>
      <p>
        u-m.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC077-Tey-cit1">
       <l>varaiyiṉiṉṟum vīḻāniṉṟatu aruvi.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
        [15]
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Kallāṭaṉār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Cuntaramūrtti</persName> 1964, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/TVG27Tolkappiyam/page/72/mode/1up">72</ref>.</p>
      <p>
        <note>itaṉaiyum aṭutta nūṟpāvaiyum iṇaittu orṉūṟpāvākak koḷvar iḷampūraṇar.</note>
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
